descriptionHTML:
That's it! If you're music passionate person you might like to try out this watch face on your wrist.

- Simple and beautiful design
- Support for interactive, ambient, low-bit, and burn-in protection modes
- Fits well on both round and circular watches

Compatible with most popular smartwatches: Moto 360, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Sony Smartwatch 3, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, LG Watch Urbane and many others.
